@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_ilierz(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v0 = 0.04
    v1 = wp.exp(0.39)
    v0 = (wp.cos((tmp + 0.74 * tmp + 0.81)) * (v1 / v0))
    v2 = (wp.cos((v0 + 0.07 - v1 + 0.48)) + wp.abs(wp.abs(tmp + 0.86)))
    data[tid] = v0
